{"title":"PHP - utf-8 strings handling","date":"2013-03-23T00:00:00.000Z","tags":"php","intro":"<p>Enable mbstring <a href=\"http://www.php.net/manual/en/mbstring.overload.php\">function overloading mode</a> and set default\nencoding for string functions to utf-8 in php.ini:</p>\n<pre><code><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span class=\"nx\">mbstring</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"nx\">internal_encoding</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"nx\">UTF</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">8</span>\n<span class=\"nx\">mbstring</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"nx\">func_overload</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"mi\">7</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n</code></pre>"}
